      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    },
    {
      "name": "dried oregano",
      "amount": "1 tsp"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350F.",
    "Line a 9x9 inch baking dish with parchment paper.",
    "In a large bowl, mix the ground oats, crumbled feta, chopped walnuts, raisins, and dried oregano.",
    "Whisk together the eggs, milk, olive oil, and honey until smooth.",
    "Pour the wet mixture over the dry ingredients and stir to combine.",
    "Fold in the fresh spinach.",
    "Transfer the mixture to the prepared baking dish and spread evenly.",
    "Bake for 40 minutes until the top is golden and the center is set.",
    "Remove from oven and let rest for 10 minutes before serving."
